{"word":"G1342 - δίκαιος - díkaios - dik'-ah-yos - Just","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δίκαιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>díkaios"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>dik'-ah-yos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Just"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"நீதிமானாயிருக்கிற, நீதியுள்ள, நியாயமான, உண்மையுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"righteous, observing divine and human laws; one who is such as he ought to be"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G1349 - δίκη - díkē - dee'-kay/1349\">G1349</a>; <i>equitable</i> (in character or act); by implication <i>innocent</i>, <i>holy</i> (absolutely or relatively): - just, meet, right (-eous)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1341 - δικαιοκρισία - dikaiokrisía - dik-ah-yok-ris-ee'-ah/1341\">G1341</a>, <a href=\"#/G1342 - δίκαιος - díkaios - dik'-ah-yos/1342\">G1342</a>, <a href=\"#/G1343 - δικαιοσύνη - dikaiosýnē - dik-ah-yos-oo'-nay/1343\">G1343</a>, <a href=\"#/G1344 - δικαιόω - dikaióō - dik-ah-yo'-o/1344\">G1344</a>, <a href=\"#/G1345 - δικαίωμα - dikaíōma - dik-ah'-yo-mah/1345\">G1345</a>, <a href=\"#/G1346 - δικαίως - dikaíōs - dik-ah'-yoce/1346\">G1346</a>, <a href=\"#/G1347 - δικαίωσις - dikaíōsis - dik-ah'-yo-sis/1347\">G1347</a>, <a href=\"#/G1349 - δίκη - díkē - dee'-kay/1349\">G1349</a>"}]}